OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Outgoing CEO says
OL,4,Che was told 'not to dig into past'
OL,6,FITV News' Ellie Pitt reports on the
OL,7,Fkey moments to emerge from Nick Read's
OL,8,Ffirst day of evidence at the Horizon
OL,9,FIT inquiry
OL,11,FThe outgoing boss of the Post Office
OL,12,Fhas told the Horizon IT inquiry he was
OL,13,Finformed not to "dig into the details
OL,14,Fof the past" by its leading lawyer
OL,15,Fwhen he first took on the job.
OL,17,FNick Read made the remarks as he gave
OL,18,Fevidence at the final phase of the
OL,19,Finquiry on Wednesday, the first of his
OL,20,Fthree days of giving evidence.
