OL,6,FHe said he was not made aware of the
OL,7,F"scale and enormity" of the scandal
OL,8,Fbefore taking the top job.
OL,10,FMr Read - who is stepping down from
OL,11,Fhis role as chief executive in March
OL,12,F2025 - joined long after the events
OL,13,Fwhich sparked the Horizon scandal,
OL,14,Fwhereby more than 900 sub-postmasters
OL,15,Fwere prosecuted for stealing, based on
OL,16,Fincorrect information from an IT
OL,17,Fsystem known as Horizon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
