OL,6,FBut when he became chief executive in
OL,7,F2019, litigation between a group of
OL,8,F555 sub-postmasters and the Post
OL,9,FOffice was just coming to a head, and
OL,10,Fthe company agreed to pay #58 million
OL,11,Fin compensation.
OL,13,FMr Read said in a witness statement
OL,14,Fdiscussed at the inquiry: "Private
OL,15,Fprosecutions were presented to me as a
OL,16,Fhistoric issue that had ceased before
OL,17,F2015 and that I did not need to dig
OL,18,Finto the details of what had happened
OL,19,Fat Post Office in the past as this
OL,20,Fconduct had ended."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
