OL,6,FHe confirmed that it was the Post
OL,7,FOffice's general counsel Ben Foat, who
OL,8,Fis temporarily away from the business,
OL,9,Fwho had told him that.
OL,11,FMr Read also denied referring to a
OL,12,Fgroup of Post Office investigators as
OL,13,F"untouchables" - staff who were
OL,14,Fshielded from the effects of the
OL,15,Finquiry.
OL,17,F"That is not an expression that is
OL,18,Fused in the organisation," he said.
