OL,6,FElsewhere, Mr Read shed light on the
OL,7,Fopinion of the Post Office, after the
OL,8,Fconvictions of hundreds of postmasters
OL,9,Fwere quashed earlier this year.
OL,11,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,12,FPolitics? Tom, Robert and Anushka dig
OL,13,Finto the biggest issues dominating the
OL,14,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,16,FHe said: "I don't think I could say
OL,17,Fspecifically that that is the case but
OL,18,Fthere will be a view that not every
OL,19,Fquashed conviction will be innocent
OL,20,Fpostmasters.
