OL,6,F"The majority of the organisation
OL,7,Fwould agree that the action that has
OL,8,Fbeen taken is absolutely the right
OL,9,Faction and whether there are guilty
OL,10,Fpostmasters that have been exonerated
OL,11,Freally is no longer an issue."
OL,13,FHe added it was "astonishing" that the
OL,14,FPost Office itself was involved in
OL,15,Fadministering compensation for wrongly-
OL,16,Fprosecuted postmasters.
OL,18,FMr Read was brought in to replace
OL,19,Fformer CEO Paula Vennells in 2019 and
OL,20,F"right the wrongs of the past".
