OL,6,FHowever, it's likely that he will also
OL,7,Fbe forced to defend his own behaviour,
OL,8,Fincluding his repeated requests for a
OL,9,Fpay rise.
OL,11,FThere have also been allegations of
OL,12,Fbullying at the company in the years
OL,13,Fafter Sir Alan Bates led the
OL,14,Fpostmasters to a 2019 High Court
OL,15,Fvictory.
OL,17,FPlus, the supposed replacement for the
OL,18,FHorizon system, the New Branch IT
OL,19,Fsystem (NBIT), has succumbed to delays
OL,20,Fand bugs.
