OL,6,FIt was originally planned for release
OL,7,Fin March 2025, but it is likely to be
OL,8,Fdelayed until mid-2026.
OL,10,FAdditionally, its projected cost has
OL,11,Fincreased from #180 million to #1.1
OL,12,Fbillion.
OL,14,FAmong Mr Read's detractors is Sir Alan
OL,15,FBates who said he did not "achieve
OL,16,Fanything" during his tenure as CEO.
